channel.description:

item.title: Testscape Compile Error
item.dc:creator: @Word8 Word8
item.description:
@Word8 wrote:

http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp
^^ go there and download “Java Runtime Environment (JRE) 5.0 Update 8” and “JDK 5.0 Update 8”

then go to start … right click my computer … properties … advanced …environment Variables…
click new …
variable name: Classpath
variable value: SET CLASSPATH=C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_08\bin;%CLASSPATH%;.

click ok …
click new …

variable name: Path
variable value: C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_08\bin;%CLASSPATH%;.

click ok …
then click ok again …
then click ok 1 more time …

it should be good then if not send me a pm and i tell you something els that you could do
